{"tid":1505101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［前中後排一齊入黎］企疏啲？到底點樣先企疏啲？","createTime":"2019-08-25T12:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:02:13.000Z","uid":284778,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"46283a8cce72fb7262eaa93abcbd2ba440107fea","tid":1505101,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:48:54.000Z","msg":"先唔講對峙呢種形式有無用<br />\n但係大家成日互屌塞死哂走唔到<br />\n我想講淨係嗌<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">企疏啲 成效極低</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為人數極多 極密集 跟住睇唔到路<br />\n最前排同後排既相距可以極遠 相隔三至四個街口 就算前線開始被推進 要傳到後排都需要好多時間<br />\n<br />\n同埋退退下 有啲人就會自己判斷嗌停 或者話夠喇 但前線可能未退得夠位<br />\n<br />\n又會嗌唔好再退喇 嗌前線唔夠人<br />\n到啲人慢慢迫番上去<br />\n但黑警又會突然推進 loop番同樣情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本無人知要企幾疏 點樣企 所以試左咁多次都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要解決 令大家夠位走 大家需要</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有陣型 有共識</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LSdLCs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LSdLCs.png&h=e03a0cbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我跪求各位前中後排<br />\n可以諗下呢個陣 試下解唔解決到<br />\n<br />\n好似大家平時分紅海咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直接預留街道既<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一半闊度做緩衝通道</span><br />\n<br />\n方便運物資，前面真係推進時候，直接用番啲緩衝空間<br />\n<br />\n唔需要嗌企疏啲嗌到死<br />\n只需要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有共識預留中間位置</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果覺得重要可以試下就幫手推<br />\n每次都拉咁多手足 好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a4f67f65c65b382d792e62002498da2c49bed2","tid":1505101,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:51:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75ddebf932c953cfb77d3d3db267a40369834719","tid":1505101,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:53:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83530150bb64c34e22bd19bcb98099910749fba9","tid":1505101,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:58:09.000Z","msg":"屌唔好煩，我去完民陣831就淨係去機場！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505122</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2d13e3cc8931aea0da1554aa284fb1bccba4c44b","tid":1505101,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf68d87aa64aa34a48924d3264309300c3f6fcf","tid":1505101,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"好野就要推"},{"pid":"ade05206f33fac01cab3b414d4e541bf90b4a6a6","tid":1505101,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:00:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"221a2322747b8d0653615d72940fe149c9cd6ac4","tid":1505101,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"好擔心深水埗既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28838cbdaf229c425653aec2c67f6b68283b132e","tid":1505101,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2a7f7e4bd756233f72eca4b96378b8b49349af","tid":1505101,"uid":34205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"可以試下"},{"pid":"75906fc19d3820920be3b309f8a2964be6ffdca0","tid":1505101,"uid":34205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a6f6ed8072bd5a9484131a968678099e0cfb464","tid":1505101,"uid":284778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img s